<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The MFN General master file notification transaction is used where the master file is a simple one that contains only a key and the text value of that key. Both values are carried in <em>MFE-4 - Primary Key Value - MFE</em>. The specific master file being updated is identified by <em>MFI-1 - Master File Identifier</em> and <em>MFI-2 - Master Files Application Identifier</em>.</p>
</div>
